[
    {
        "text": "(knife tapping)",
        "start": 0.176,
        "duration": 1.069
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat music)",
        "start": 1.245,
        "duration": 2.265
    },
    {
        "text": "- Hi, everybody!",
        "start": 3.51,
        "duration": 1.69
    },
    {
        "text": "How are you doing these days?",
        "start": 5.2,
        "duration": 1.67
    },
    {
        "text": "Today, I'm going to show\nyou how to make galbi-jjim,",
        "start": 6.87,
        "duration": 3.91
    },
    {
        "text": "braised beef short ribs.",
        "start": 10.78,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "I always say that, \"Oh,\nthis is a very easy recipe,\"",
        "start": 12.82,
        "duration": 3.47
    },
    {
        "text": "but today's not very easy",
        "start": 16.29,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "but if you learn about this recipe,",
        "start": 18.63,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "you will be really showing\noff your cooking skill.",
        "start": 21.27,
        "duration": 3.37
    },
    {
        "text": "This dish is usually made\non special occasions.",
        "start": 24.64,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Whenever I want to impress\nsome people, I make this.",
        "start": 28.18,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a really centerpiece,\nreally beautiful,",
        "start": 31.46,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "and with some kimchi,\n more side dishes,",
        "start": 34.9,
        "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
        "text": "and rice and soup.",
        "start": 37.98,
        "duration": 1.27
    },
    {
        "text": "It will be a perfect Korean table setting.",
        "start": 39.25,
        "duration": 2.89
    },
    {
        "text": "So, let's start!",
        "start": 42.14,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm using 2 pounds of beef short ribs.",
        "start": 43.8,
        "duration": 3.48
    },
    {
        "text": "I just soaked these in cold\nwater, just around one hour,",
        "start": 47.28,
        "duration": 3.69
    },
    {
        "text": "and I changed the water, so\nI removed all the blood.",
        "start": 50.97,
        "duration": 2.813
    },
    {
        "text": "Lots of meat is attached.",
        "start": 55.99,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "Good quality beef short ribs.",
        "start": 57.87,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "So now, I'm going to blanch.",
        "start": 60.69,
        "duration": 2.113
    },
    {
        "text": "I will blanch for 5 minutes.",
        "start": 69.04,
        "duration": 1.883
    },
    {
        "text": "5 minutes passed!",
        "start": 72.01,
        "duration": 2.15
    },
    {
        "text": "See, lots of bubbles!  Let's wash.",
        "start": 74.16,
        "duration": 4.271
    },
    {
        "text": "Turn off.",
        "start": 78.431,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "I will use this pot to cook today",
        "start": 100.42,
        "duration": 2.15
    },
    {
        "text": "and it's nicely washed.",
        "start": 103.55,
        "duration": 1.803
    },
    {
        "text": "Just a little more than 2 pounds.",
        "start": 108.81,
        "duration": 2.45
    },
    {
        "text": "This is for 4 servings.",
        "start": 111.26,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "So this is 8 pieces.",
        "start": 113.16,
        "duration": 1.94
    },
    {
        "text": "Kind of, you know, for me, 1 piece is enough.",
        "start": 115.1,
        "duration": 2.91
    },
    {
        "text": "These are 8  pieces.",
        "start": 118.01,
        "duration": 1.31
    },
    {
        "text": "I think 4 servings is okay",
        "start": 119.32,
        "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
        "text": "because we are going to add",
        "start": 121.34,
        "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
        "text": "a lot of vegetables. You'll see.",
        "start": 123.04,
        "duration": 2.62
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, I will just add this here.",
        "start": 125.66,
        "duration": 1.933
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, we have to make\nsauce, seasoning sauce.",
        "start": 129.17,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "1/3 cup soy sauce.",
        "start": 134.21,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "I use mirim (mirin), it's cooking wine.",
        "start": 136.43,
        "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
        "text": "1/2 cup mirim.",
        "start": 139.33,
        "duration": 1.173
    },
    {
        "text": "Instead of sugar, I'll use Swerve.",
        "start": 142.18,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a zero calorie kind of\nsugar replacement.",
        "start": 145.3,
        "duration": 3.82
    },
    {
        "text": "But you can use also just\nwhite sugar or brown sugar",
        "start": 149.12,
        "duration": 3.89
    },
    {
        "text": "but I will use this Swerve 1/4 cup.",
        "start": 153.01,
        "duration": 3.073
    },
    {
        "text": "I soaked these mushrooms.",
        "start": 159.23,
        "duration": 2.061
    },
    {
        "text": "Shiitake mushrooms, soaked in water.",
        "start": 161.291,
        "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
        "text": "One.",
        "start": 164.33,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Squeeze out a  little bit.",
        "start": 168.26,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "So 2 cups.",
        "start": 171.3,
        "duration": 1.633
    },
    {
        "text": "2 cups mushroom soaking water.",
        "start": 174.272,
        "duration": 2.318
    },
    {
        "text": "Really, really soft now.",
        "start": 176.59,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "I soaked 4 hours in cold water.",
        "start": 178.24,
        "duration": 3.02
    },
    {
        "text": "I brought my garlic and ginger.",
        "start": 181.26,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "8 cloves of garlic and\naround 1 teaspoon ginger.",
        "start": 183.38,
        "duration": 3.91
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm going to mince all these.",
        "start": 187.29,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "Before that I will add\nground black pepper,",
        "start": 189.3,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "around 1/2  teaspoon.",
        "start": 193.2,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's mince garlic and ginger.",
        "start": 195.24,
        "duration": 2.307
    },
    {
        "text": "This is ginger.",
        "start": 199.961,
        "duration": 1.333
    },
    {
        "text": "Mix well.",
        "start": 216.16,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "And I'm going add this here.",
        "start": 220.91,
        "duration": 1.947
    },
    {
        "text": "You see?",
        "start": 224.08,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Lots of seasonings.",
        "start": 226.153,
        "duration": 1.827
    },
    {
        "text": "And cover this, turn on the heat,",
        "start": 227.98,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "cook for 20 minutes over medium-high heat.",
        "start": 231.02,
        "duration": 2.573
    },
    {
        "text": "When you see it's boiling, I'm going\nto turn down the heat to low",
        "start": 234.926,
        "duration": 3.654
    },
    {
        "text": "and then I will add these guys.",
        "start": 238.58,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "With carrot, I made these balls.",
        "start": 240.8,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "I will show you how to make this ball,",
        "start": 242.93,
        "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
        "text": "and radish.",
        "start": 244.95,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "And this is soaked shiitake\nmushrooms and also chestnuts.",
        "start": 246.39,
        "duration": 4.45
    },
    {
        "text": "We need around 12 balls.",
        "start": 250.84,
        "duration": 2.693
    },
    {
        "text": "Around  1.5 inches.",
        "start": 255.384,
        "duration": 3.706
    },
    {
        "text": "I already made nine balls,",
        "start": 259.09,
        "duration": 1.67
    },
    {
        "text": "so I'm going to show you 3 more.",
        "start": 260.76,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "And just make balls.",
        "start": 263.56,
        "duration": 1.723
    },
    {
        "text": "Shape it into a ball.",
        "start": 272.32,
        "duration": 1.483
    },
    {
        "text": "Like this.",
        "start": 278.05,
        "duration": 1.193
    },
    {
        "text": "Take off a stem.",
        "start": 288.393,
        "duration": 3.897
    },
    {
        "text": "With all this leftover stuff,",
        "start": 292.29,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "later you are going to make stir-fried rice.",
        "start": 293.89,
        "duration": 2.933
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's make radish ball.",
        "start": 310.18,
        "duration": 1.713
    },
    {
        "text": "Cut into around 1.5 inch.",
        "start": 314.2,
        "duration": 3.149
    },
    {
        "text": "About 1.5 inch chunk.",
        "start": 332.355,
        "duration": 4.583
    },
    {
        "text": "See, with this one, also make a ball.",
        "start": 339.44,
        "duration": 3.753
    },
    {
        "text": "With this leftover, all these bits,",
        "start": 351.16,
        "duration": 2.99
    },
    {
        "text": "it'll be awesome if you make stock,",
        "start": 354.15,
        "duration": 2.26
    },
    {
        "text": "an anchovy kelp stock\nor vegetable stock.",
        "start": 356.41,
        "duration": 2.91
    },
    {
        "text": "We also use chestnuts.",
        "start": 359.32,
        "duration": 1.733
    },
    {
        "text": "I got this chestnut\nfrom a Korean store.",
        "start": 362.151,
        "duration": 3.019
    },
    {
        "text": "It's already peeled, fresh\nfrozen. These are fresh chestnuts.",
        "start": 365.17,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "I will show you how to peel this. \nBecause chestnuts are",
        "start": 369.57,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "not available all the time,\nyou can use these frozen chestnuts.",
        "start": 372.3,
        "duration": 4.237
    },
    {
        "text": "It's  vacuum packed.",
        "start": 377.651,
        "duration": 1.732
    },
    {
        "text": "I will also add dozen.",
        "start": 382.13,
        "duration": 1.943
    },
    {
        "text": "Now  20 minutes already passed,\nI'm going to add these guys.",
        "start": 389.66,
        "duration": 4.083
    },
    {
        "text": "Carrot balls, radish,\nchestnut, mushroom, all.",
        "start": 396.218,
        "duration": 4.432
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm going to cook this over low\nheat and simmer for 1 hour.",
        "start": 405.43,
        "duration": 4.37
    },
    {
        "text": "But I need to open",
        "start": 409.8,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "and stir this occasionally.",
        "start": 411.81,
        "duration": 2.09
    },
    {
        "text": "The radish has a lot of water,\nso delicious water comes out from it.",
        "start": 413.9,
        "duration": 3.98
    },
    {
        "text": "and also all these are  well\ncooked and the ribs,",
        "start": 417.88,
        "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
        "text": "these beef short ribs are\ngoing to be so tender.",
        "start": 422.52,
        "duration": 2.53
    },
    {
        "text": "We need to cook this over low heat.",
        "start": 425.05,
        "duration": 2.38
    },
    {
        "text": "As I told you, I'm going\nto peel this one chestnut",
        "start": 427.43,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "to show you how to do.",
        "start": 430.79,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Top part and pointed part and then cut.",
        "start": 432.05,
        "duration": 3.987
    },
    {
        "text": "Then both sides, peel like this.",
        "start": 441.951,
        "duration": 2.667
    },
    {
        "text": "Then, just easy.",
        "start": 451.73,
        "duration": 2.043
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 455.35,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Then remove all this brown stuff.",
        "start": 457.27,
        "duration": 3.333
    },
    {
        "text": "Look at that!  So pretty!",
        "start": 467.68,
        "duration": 1.81
    },
    {
        "text": "This way, you can peel this if you want",
        "start": 469.49,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "to shell this at home. \nBut if it's too much hassle,",
        "start": 472.04,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "just use frozen chestnuts.",
        "start": 475.46,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Which is more tasty?",
        "start": 478.06,
        "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
        "text": "Of course, these fresh\nchestnuts are more tasty.",
        "start": 479.81,
        "duration": 3.613
    },
    {
        "text": "I will show you other ingredients.",
        "start": 486.0,
        "duration": 2.09
    },
    {
        "text": "Ginkgo nuts.",
        "start": 488.09,
        "duration": 1.09
    },
    {
        "text": "Ginkgo nuts and pine nuts.",
        "start": 489.18,
        "duration": 2.89
    },
    {
        "text": "Whenever I go to Chinatown,",
        "start": 492.07,
        "duration": 1.73
    },
    {
        "text": "there are some ladies\nsitting on the sidewalk",
        "start": 493.8,
        "duration": 3.05
    },
    {
        "text": "and they always sell these.",
        "start": 496.85,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "These ginkgo nuts.",
        "start": 498.77,
        "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
        "text": "They probably must have harvested these ginkgo nuts",
        "start": 500.07,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "just before winter time\nand they probably kept",
        "start": 502.51,
        "duration": 3.53
    },
    {
        "text": "in their own freezer and\nthen brought some of them.",
        "start": 506.04,
        "duration": 3.69
    },
    {
        "text": "So I could buy even in the summertime.",
        "start": 509.73,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "and it's so cheap, cheap price!",
        "start": 512.06,
        "duration": 2.45
    },
    {
        "text": "I brought home and then I froze these.",
        "start": 514.51,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "These days, Korean store,\nsell frozen ginkgo nuts.",
        "start": 516.76,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "This is also vacuum packed.",
        "start": 523.59,
        "duration": 4.613
    },
    {
        "text": "You see?",
        "start": 531.738,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "I put some cooking oil.",
        "start": 537.87,
        "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
        "text": "Just add some.",
        "start": 539.62,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "Stir these.",
        "start": 542.203,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "(nuts sizzling)",
        "start": 543.036,
        "duration": 3.347
    },
    {
        "text": "Add some salt so that the\nskin is easily removed",
        "start": 546.383,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "and also make it a little bit\nsalty and tasty.",
        "start": 553.393,
        "duration": 3.347
    },
    {
        "text": "When this is cooked, it looks a little bit translucent.",
        "start": 556.74,
        "duration": 4.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Little salt.",
        "start": 568.977,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Nice! Turn off.",
        "start": 574.586,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "And then I've gotta remove the skin like this.",
        "start": 580.3,
        "duration": 2.787
    },
    {
        "text": "And you will see the nice,\nclean ginkgo nuts.",
        "start": 584.11,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, we have to use just these 3\nitems.",
        "start": 608.657,
        "duration": 3.473
    },
    {
        "text": "Pine nuts and ginkgo nuts.",
        "start": 612.13,
        "duration": 3.11
    },
    {
        "text": "They are going to\nbe last minute garnish.",
        "start": 615.24,
        "duration": 3.14
    },
    {
        "text": "But we need to cook this.",
        "start": 618.38,
        "duration": 2.328
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a jujube.",
        "start": 620.708,
        "duration": 1.222
    },
    {
        "text": "I use 8 large jujubes.",
        "start": 621.93,
        "duration": 2.65
    },
    {
        "text": "Just cut like this and you\nwill feel some hard stuff,",
        "start": 625.628,
        "duration": 4.632
    },
    {
        "text": "that's the seed, and cut around the seed.",
        "start": 630.26,
        "duration": 4.303
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a seed.",
        "start": 636.36,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Like this.",
        "start": 638.19,
        "duration": 2.613
    },
    {
        "text": "All these ingredients are now ready.",
        "start": 641.94,
        "duration": 2.47
    },
    {
        "text": "Meanwhile, keep stirring,",
        "start": 644.41,
        "duration": 1.81
    },
    {
        "text": "once in awhile.",
        "start": 646.22,
        "duration": 1.486
    },
    {
        "text": "(upbeat music)",
        "start": 647.706,
        "duration": 2.583
    },
    {
        "text": "1 hour passed.",
        "start": 657.11,
        "duration": 1.563
    },
    {
        "text": "Look at that!",
        "start": 660.384,
        "duration": 0.859
    },
    {
        "text": "Wow!",
        "start": 661.243,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "Everything looks so tender.",
        "start": 662.623,
        "duration": 2.31
    },
    {
        "text": "Ribs look really tender now.",
        "start": 666.01,
        "duration": 2.913
    },
    {
        "text": "I will add jujubes.",
        "start": 670.38,
        "duration": 2.033
    },
    {
        "text": "jujube.",
        "start": 673.51,
        "duration": 0.99
    },
    {
        "text": "I need to glaze this to make shiny.",
        "start": 676.78,
        "duration": 2.68
    },
    {
        "text": "I will add some rice syrup,\naround 2 tablespoons.",
        "start": 679.46,
        "duration": 3.273
    },
    {
        "text": "And simmer another 10 minutes,\nthen galbi-jjim is done!",
        "start": 689.16,
        "duration": 4.463
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm so excited!",
        "start": 696.07,
        "duration": 1.57
    },
    {
        "text": "My galbi-jjim should be done now.",
        "start": 697.64,
        "duration": 2.253
    },
    {
        "text": "Nice!",
        "start": 703.28,
        "duration": 1.364
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, I'm going to turn up the heat.",
        "start": 704.644,
        "duration": 1.949
    },
    {
        "text": "High heat, so I want to boil off",
        "start": 707.77,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "all this broth to make it shiny.",
        "start": 711.85,
        "duration": 2.523
    },
    {
        "text": "Ladle some broth and put it over top.",
        "start": 715.33,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "(food sizzling)",
        "start": 721.574,
        "duration": 2.667
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, done!",
        "start": 742.47,
        "duration": 0.917
    },
    {
        "text": "Turn off.",
        "start": 744.29,
        "duration": 1.373
    },
    {
        "text": "Ginkgo nuts.",
        "start": 749.59,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Pine nuts.",
        "start": 752.86,
        "duration": 1.003
    },
    {
        "text": "This is galbi-jjim, very special food.",
        "start": 759.6,
        "duration": 2.99
    },
    {
        "text": "Special party food.",
        "start": 762.59,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "Let me taste!",
        "start": 764.23,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "This is mushroom.",
        "start": 765.99,
        "duration": 1.153
    },
    {
        "text": "Radish.",
        "start": 768.34,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Radish ball is very tasty.",
        "start": 769.34,
        "duration": 1.883
    },
    {
        "text": "Mm!",
        "start": 775.235,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh my!",
        "start": 776.95,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Sweet and very juicy.",
        "start": 779.82,
        "duration": 2.09
